n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"gnav__list\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"gnav__list__item\"><a href=\"service.html\">サービス紹介</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"gnav__list__item\"><a href=\"recruit.html\">採用情報</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"gnav__list__item\"><a href=\"company.html\">会社案内</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"gnav__list__item\"><a href=\"group.html\">グループ会社</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"gnav__list__item snsicon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tsuyamagroup/?hl=ja\" target=\"_blank\"><img\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"img/ig_icon.png\" alt=\"Instagram\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsuyamagroup/\" target=\"_blank\"><img\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"img/fb_icon.png\" alt=\"Facebook\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gnav-contact\"><a href=\"mailto:info@tsuyamagroup.co.jp\">お問い合わせ</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gnav-overlay js-nav-overlay hidden-pc\"></div>\n\t\t\t</nav>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"homeMainimg\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"homeMainimg-mainTxt\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"homeMainimg-mainTxt-in\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeMainimg-mainTxt__en f-oswald\">EAT <br class=\"hidden-pc\">FOR <br class=\"hidden-pc\">LIFE\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeMainimg-mainTxt__txt\">津山商店は皆様の<br class=\"hidden-pc\">笑顔・健康・喜びのために<br>美味しく安心していただける<br\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"hidden-pc\">お食事を提供いたします</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/main_img01_pc.png\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\" class=\"homeMainimg__img hidden-sp\">\n\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/main_img01_sp.png\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\" class=\"homeMainimg__img hidden-pc\">\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"navBtn js-nav-btn hidden-pc\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>\n\t</header>\n\n\t<main>\n\n\t\t<section class=\"homeIntro\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"c-inner01\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"homeIntro__icoImg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/ico_kouken01.svg\" alt=\"「食」を通じて社会貢献\">\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"homeIntro__tit\"><img src=\"assets/img/home/txt_kouken01_2.svg\" alt=\"「食」を通じて社会貢献を\"></h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeIntro__txt\">津山商店は『食』にこだわるトータルフードカンパニーです。<br\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"hidden-sp\">地域に根ざし、時代と共に変わりゆく食のニーズに応え、<br\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"hidden-sp\">福祉施設・病院・保育園・学校・事業所等の食事提供を行っています。<br\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"hidden-sp\">食べる方の喜び・笑顔・健康維持の為に、『安全・安心で美味しい食事』を提供し続けること、<br\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"hidden-sp\">地域の人・産物・資源を大切に、新しい価値を創造していくことが私たちの使命です。</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"homeIntro__bgImg\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/bg_kouken02.png\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t<!-- .homeIntro -->\n\n\t\t<section class=\"homeService\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"homeService-inner c-inner02\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"homeService__tit c-tit01 is-center\"><span class=\"c-tit01__en\">SERVICE</span>サービス案内</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"homeService-list\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"homeService-list__item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"service.html#service01\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/img_service01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"homeService-list__item__img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeService-list__item__tit\"><img src=\"assets/img/ico_service01.svg\" alt=\"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"homeService-list__item__tit-ico\">福祉施設</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"homeService-list__item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"service.html#service02\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/img_service02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"homeService-list__item__img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeService-list__item__tit\"><img src=\"assets/img/ico_service02.svg\" alt=\"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"homeService-list__item__tit-ico\">病院・医療施設</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"homeService-list__item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"service.html#service03\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/img_service03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"homeService-list__item__img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeService-list__item__tit\"><img src=\"assets/img/ico_service03.svg\" alt=\"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"homeService-list__item__tit-ico\">学校</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"homeService-list__item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"service.html#service04\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/img_service04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"homeService-list__item__img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeService-list__item__tit\"><img src=\"assets/img/ico_service04.svg\" alt=\"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"homeService-list__item__tit-ico\">事業所</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"homeService-list__item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"service.html#service05\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/home/img_service05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"homeService-list__item__img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeService-list__item__tit\"><img src=\"assets/img/ico_service05.svg\" alt=\"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"homeService-list__item__tit-ico\">その他</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t<!-- .homeService -->\n\n\t\t<section class=\"homeRecruit\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"homeRecruit-inner c-inner02\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"homeRecruit-imgBox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"90%\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mkJ7vieee6I\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- <img src=\"assets/img/home/bg_recruit01.png\" alt=\"\"> -->\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"homeRecruit-txtBox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"homeRecruit__tit c-tit01\"><span class=\"c-tit01__en\">RECRUIT</span>採用情報</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"homeRecruit__txt\">給食の調理や食事を通じて<br class=\"hidden-sp\">地域福祉のお仕事に興味がある方大歓迎です。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"imgIco\" src=\"assets/img/home/bg_recruit_ico.png\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"homeRecruit-more c-btn01\"><a href=\"recruit.html\">詳しく見る</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t<!-- .homeRecruit -->\n\n\t</main><!-- main -->\n\n\t<footer class=\"footer\">\n\t\t<div class=\"pagetop js-pagetop\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"assets/img/ico_retop.svg\" alt=\"TOP\"></a></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"footer-inner\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"footer-box01\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"footer__logo\"><img src=\"assets/img/header-logo.png\" alt=\"株式会社 津山商店\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"fotterLogo\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- <div class=\"sgsiso\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"assets/img/bnr01.jpg\" alt=\"ISO9001:2008認証取得\" class=\"footer__bnr\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>支店における受託給食調理業務の管理<br>本社における事業所の業務管理</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div> -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"happypartner\"><img src=\"assets/img/happypartner_logo.png\" alt=\"happypartner_logo\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"fotter__bnr\"> </div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"footer-contact\"><a href=\"mailto:info@tsuyamagroup.co.jp\">お問い合わせ</a></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"footer-box02\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"footer__address\">〒949-7302　新潟県南魚沼市浦佐5582番地1　　<br class=\"hidden-pc\">TEL：025-788-0521　　<br\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"hidden-pc\">FAX：025-788-0522</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"footer__privacy\"><a href=\"privacy.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">プライバシーポリシー</a></p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<p class=\"footer__copyright f-kalam\">Copyright &copy; TSUYAMA Group Co.,Ltd.<br class=\"hidden-pc\">All Rights\n\t\t\tReserved.</p>\n\t</footer>\n\n\t<script src=\"assets/js/jquery-3.4.1.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"assets/js/common.js\"></script>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>","finalUrl":"http://www.tsuyamagroup.co.jp/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T17:51:01.614Z"}